$CATEGORY: Vocabulary/HansenQuinn/5

::Q001::[markdown]not:{
	~%-100%ὡς#Incorrect. **ὡς** means “in order that” (Chapter 8).
	~%-100%ἅτε; οἷα#Incorrect. **ἅτε; οἷα** means “in as much as” (Chapter 8).
	~%-100%χάριν#Incorrect. **χάριν** means “for the sake of” (Chapter 6).
	~%-100%καί… καί#Incorrect. **καί… καί** means “both… and” (Chapter 1).
	~%100%μή#Correct: **οὐ; οὐκ; οὐχ (adv.)** → “not” (Chapter 2).
}


::Q002::[markdown]πέπεισμαι:{
	~%-100%leave behind#Incorrect. **λείπω** is Principal Part 1 of **λείπω** “leave behind” (Chapter 7).
	~%100%(middle) obey#Correct: **πέπεισμαι** is Principal Part 5 of **πείθω** “(middle) obey” (Chapter 5).
	~%-100%leave#Incorrect. **λείπω** is Principal Part 1 of **λείπω** “leave” (Chapter 7).
	~%-100%teach#Incorrect. **παιδεύω** is Principal Part 1 of **παιδεύω** “teach” (Chapter 2).
	~%-100%hurt#Incorrect. **βλάπτω** is Principal Part 1 of **βλάπτω** “hurt” (Chapter 5).
}


::Q003::[markdown]ἔταξα:{
	~%-100%teach#Incorrect. **παιδεύω** is Principal Part 1 of **παιδεύω** “teach” (Chapter 2).
	~%-100%command (+ gen)#Incorrect. **ἄρχω** is Principal Part 1 of **ἄρχω** “command (+ gen)” (Chapter 5).
	~%-100%harm#Incorrect. **βλάπτω** is Principal Part 1 of **βλάπτω** “harm” (Chapter 5).
	~%100%draw up (in battle)#Correct: **ἔταξα** is Principal Part 3 of **τάττω** “draw up (in battle)” (Chapter 4).
}


::Q004::[markdown]ἔπεισα:{
	~%-100%arrange, order#Incorrect. **τάττω** is Principal Part 1 of **τάττω** “arrange, order” (Chapter 4).
	~%-100%hurt#Incorrect. **βλάπτω** is Principal Part 1 of **βλάπτω** “hurt” (Chapter 5).
	~%-100%command#Incorrect. **κελεύω** is Principal Part 1 of **κελεύω** “command” (Chapter 2).
	~%100%(middle) obey#Correct: **ἔπεισα** is Principal Part 3 of **πείθω** “(middle) obey” (Chapter 5).
	~%-100%command (+ gen)#Incorrect. **ἄρχω** is Principal Part 1 of **ἄρχω** “command (+ gen)” (Chapter 5).
}


::Q005::[markdown]ἱκανός, ἱκανή, ἱκανόν:{
	~%-100%another#Incorrect. **ἄλλος, ἄλλη, ἄλλον** means “another” (Chapter 7).
	~%-100%obvious#Incorrect. **δῆλος, δήλη, δῆλον** means “obvious” (Chapter 7).
	~%100%sufficient#Correct: **ἱκανός, ἱκανή, ἱκανόν** → “capable” (Chapter 5).
	~%-100%old#Incorrect. **παλαιός, παλαιά, παλαιόν** means “old” (Chapter 6).
	~%-100%experienced in (+ gen.)#Incorrect. **ἔμπειρος, ἔμπειρον** means “experienced in (+ gen.)” (Chapter 9).
}


::Q006::[markdown]πράττω:{
	~%-100%have come#Incorrect. **ἥκω** is Principal Part 1 of **ἥκω** “have come” (Chapter 8).
	~%-100%make#Incorrect. **ποιέω** is Principal Part 1 of **ποιέω** “make” (Chapter 9).
	~%-100%to wrong#Incorrect. **ἀδικέω** is Principal Part 1 of **ἀδικέω** “to wrong” (Chapter 9).
	~%-100%conduct the government#Incorrect. **πολῑτεύω** is Principal Part 1 of **πολῑτεύω** “conduct the government” (Chapter 6).
	~%100%do#Correct: **πράττω** is Principal Part 1 of **πράττω** “do” (Chapter 5).
}


