	~%100%unbind#Correct: **λύσω** is Principal Part 2 of **λύω** “unbind” (Chapter 2).
	~%-100%do#Incorrect. **πράττω** is Principal Part 1 of **πράττω** “do” (Chapter 5).
	~%-100%command#Incorrect. **κελεύω** is Principal Part 1 of **κελεύω** “command” (Chapter 2).
	~%-100%bury#Incorrect. **θάπτω** is Principal Part 1 of **θάπτω** “bury” (Chapter 4).
}


