	~%-100%do wrong#Incorrect. **ἀδικέω** is Principal Part 1 of **ἀδικέω** “do wrong” (Chapter 9).
	~%100%do#Correct: **πράξω** is Principal Part 2 of **πράττω** “do” (Chapter 5).
	~%-100%command#Incorrect. **κελεύω** is Principal Part 1 of **κελεύω** “command” (Chapter 2).
}


